        <abstract>
            <p>Thinks the facts in Fritz Müller’s letter could be published.</p> 
<p>Recommends August Weismann’s essay on dimorphism ["Über den Saison-Dimorphismus der Schmetterlinge", <hi rend="italic">Studien zur Descendenz-Theorie</hi> 1 (1875)]</p> 
            <p>and has no doubt that intermediate forms could be eliminated as RM suggests.</p>
        </abstract>
